properties.description: Detour #9: Marathon (miles 17) and Half Marathon (mile 3 + 4): Waterfront Warehouse district From 8:45am to 12:30pm: If you live east of Jackson, head down Madison, take a right on 5th to I-880 southbound. If you need to head northbound, get off at the next exit (16th Avenue) take right on Embarcadero to get to Jack London Square. Or to get to I-880 northbound, take left on Embarcadero, follow it around for about a mile past Union Point Park, it will turn into East 7th Street, take a left on 23rd Avenue and follow signs back to I-880 Northbound. If you live west of Jackson, take 4th Street westbound, left on Broadway and follow the signs to I-880 southbound. Or stay on 4th Street, right on Castro to get to I-980 northbound. After 12:30pm: Runners will have cleared area; streets will be reopened to normal traffic.
